    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="post__meta">Last updated: June 22, 2026</p>
  </header>

  <div class="post__content">
    <p>
      This privacy policy applies to software published by Mangla &amp; Co LLC, a Virginia limited liability company operated by Moeed Ahmad.
    </p>

    <h2>Local-First Software</h2>
    <p>
      Mangla &amp; Co LLC builds small macOS utilities that are designed to process your files and data locally on your own device. Unless a specific application states otherwise, these tools do not send your documents, messages, databases, prompts, or usage activity to Mangla &amp; Co LLC servers.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>
      Applications published by Mangla &amp; Co LLC do not collect, store, sell, rent, or monetize personal data, application analytics data, user files, or application usage history unless a future app-specific notice explicitly says otherwise.
    </p>

    <h2>Blue Bubble Vault</h2>
    <p>
      Blue Bubble Vault processes selected Apple Messages / iMessage / SMS / RCS data locally on the user's Mac. The app does not upload message contents, Contacts data, local Messages databases, local backup databases, export files, or app usage history to Mangla &amp; Co LLC.
    </p>
    <p>
      Full Disk Access is used only when the user chooses to access live local Messages data. Contacts access is optional and used locally to resolve display names. Exports are written only to a user-selected location. Demo mode uses synthetic sample data and does not require private Messages, Contacts, backup, or Full Disk Access permissions.
    </p>
    <p>
      Blue Bubble Vault exports, including PDFs, CSV files, manifest files, diagnostic HTML sidecars, and any copied attachments, may contain private message content and should be handled as sensitive files by the user.
    </p>

    <h2>Website Analytics and App Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      This website may use Google Analytics or similar site analytics to understand website traffic and basic page usage. That website analytics is separate from the macOS applications published by Mangla &amp; Co LLC.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Blue Bubble Vault app itself does not include analytics or telemetry unless a future version explicitly says otherwise.
    </p>

    <h2>Third Parties</h2>
    <p>
      Because these applications are designed to run locally and do not transmit your application data to external services, Mangla &amp; Co LLC does not provide your application data to third-party processors, advertisers, analytics providers, or data brokers.
    </p>

    <h2>Support Communications</h2>
    <p>
      If you contact Mangla &amp; Co LLC for support, the information you choose to include in that message will be used only to respond to your request. Please do not send passwords, private keys, authentication tokens, financial records, legal documents, or other sensitive files unless they are necessary for support and you are comfortable sharing them.
    </p>

